Frequently Asked Questions

1. Are your handbags made of real leather or synthetic materials?

We take pride in using high-quality materials to ensure durability, longevity, and a luxurious feel in every handbag we create. Our bags are made from genuine leather offering a timeless appeal, exquisite texture, and superior craftsmanship.

We take pride in using high-quality materials to ensure durability, longevity, and a luxurious feel in every handbag we create. Our bags are made from genuine leather offering a timeless appeal, exquisite texture, and superior craftsmanship.

2. What are the dimensions of your handbags?

Our handbags come in four different sizes to accommodate various preferences and needs. The smaller size measures 9.8 inches in width, 7.8 inches in height, and 5 inches in depth (25cm x 20cm x 13cm). This compact option offers a stylish and practical solution for carrying your essentials while maintaining a sleek and streamlined look.

 

For those who require a bit more room, we also offer a larger handbag size. This size measures 11.8 inches in width, 9.25 inches in height, and 6.3 inches in depth (30cm x 23.5cm x 16cm).

We've recently introduced larger handbags, with dimensions of 13.8 inches in width, 11.8 inches in height, and 7.5 inches in depth (35cm x 30cm x 19cm), is perfect for busy days, offering ample room for more than just the basics while still looking fashionable and polished. 

 

Our newly added extra-large handbag, measuring 15.75 inches in width, 13 inches in height, and 8.3 inches in depth (40cm x 33cm x 21cm), is designed for those who prioritize maximum capacity and functionality, making it ideal for long trips, workdays, or as a stylish carry-on that can hold everything you need with ease. Each size in our collection is crafted to meet specific needs, ensuring you find the perfect handbag that complements your lifestyle and fashion sense.

3. Are the handbag colors true to the website?

The colors of our handbags are 100% true to what's displayed on our website's product images. We take great care to ensure that the colors depicted online accurately represent the actual colors of our handbags.

4. Are more handbag colors available?

While the color options currently listed on our website showcase our existing inventory, we are excited to inform you that we do have additional color variants available for our handbags that are not yet featured on the site. We're currently in the process of updating our product listings with new images from our latest photoshoot, which will include these additional color options.

5. What accessories come with your handbags?

Each handbag is delivered as shown in the product pictures and comes with a padlock and a detachable strap. These accessories are carefully selected to complement the design and functionality of our handbags, providing versatility and added style to your carrying options.

6. What are your shipping rates?

For your convenience, we ship worldwide and offer insured and tracked shipping. For orders above $300, we offer free shipping. It generally takes 24-48 hours to process and dispatch your order.

7. Do I need to pay customs or import fees?

No, we take care of all customs and import fees.

7. I adore your handbags, but what if it doesn't complement my style?

Any brand new product can be returned for a full refund within 30 days of delivery. We offer easy returns for all domestic and international orders.
